{"tid":1685153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"高院頒臨時禁令　禁網上煽動武力傷人或毀財物","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:42:28.000Z","uid":269077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d554b58744d17c56e74b6e5a137a0c2a7deb5a0","tid":1685153,"uid":269077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沒有英國人香港只是一篤屎同尿.這就是香港脫英華治之惡果<br />\n<br />\n高院頒臨時禁令 禁網上煽動武力傷人或毀財物<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201910/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201910%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A23.jpg&h=76163512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律政司以公眾利益守護者身份，今日（10月31日）向法庭申請臨時禁制令，禁止任何人在網上及其他平台，包括但不限連登和Telegram，有意圖散布、傳播、發布、重新發布任何資訊或材料，促進、鼓勵或煽動任何人威脅使用武力，非法對他人身體或財物造成損害。 法官聽取律政司代表陳詞後，決定頒發臨時禁制令，禁制令有效至11月15日案件提訊。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-31-2019/57171?fbclid=IwAR1JYA1hvfPyfDqLRuUwoTW9PO218PwFZ8d5nvT8aajofqmuxDVGBa6Y4YI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-31-2019%2F57171%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1JYA1hvfPyfDqLRuUwoTW9PO218PwFZ8d5nvT8aajofqmuxDVGBa6Y4YI&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=25d03ca5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-31-2019/57171?fbclid=IwAR1JYA1hvfPyfDqLRuUwoTW9PO218PwFZ8d5nvT8aajofqmuxDVGBa6Y4YI</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"934f5563258cad0a742dde6e0358ea7c1d7c943b","tid":1685153,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"（公投）11.2好似有活動撞左時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手入嚟睇下討論下推下啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}